## Changelog
### Features
* 9be622abee10c59b6e52b6595c28e7a4af5069e5 feat: Extend squote template func to handle more types
* fe2dba7aee848dcd10a28482c6c2166a6a3d9641 feat: Extend quote and quoteList template funcs to handle more types
* 35148c7ea6905743836225644cd4b0cfaadfc603 feat: Add common --parent-dirs/-P flag
### Fixes
* 75e1a52c5b0727ce0e53aa4b4a175a79b67d77ea fix: Persist results of calls to GitHub API
* a8dda7867215a31251f33acbc96ed57e10ebd80f fix: Fix completion for 'archive --format'
* 3fd20e9b745a1f41ba59e3a12904fdf519359aba fix: Fix includeTemplate template func search path in init
* 5b73a4d496eaa653c6eb39f1a319f8c2167112ce fix: Accept only supported values to 'unmanaged --path-style'
* 264f34f33f2708769373c35a1c7e4048ad16a4b9 fix: Fix incorrect config template change warnings
* 8ba1988d472246f7f60709e6074c64e8531ea3ed fix: Fix panic when --keep-going is set
* 2d0fa361d210f40d76da9ec4fcc4738b32e35e5e fix: Fix panic when running chattr on externals
* d28823de7fb5edbc71e93c90357d2d228c1b8dbb fix: Use builtin age when encryption is unset
### Documentation updates
* 554ff274a23693db911e8fac6292a005d0dfecca docs: Replace common flags descriptions with snippets
* b8610d493ab06b832a8a924bbf59310c22d37a83 docs: Fill reference title page
* 2a41aeb8d9d958e34ae5ef41686907492c228af2 docs: Update "how scripts work" section
* 6e9281d6fe14d80b2b44beea4593a9a66c91844a docs: Update shell completions section
* 947e88e70f2df8cd44e1a9a0ea7b664dc6dfd0f0 docs: Improvements for command flags description
* 56729ce4f1b880c4068be1ae3a8de1ebef8af552 docs: Automatically check that all flags are documented
* 0fb4392222092155e0d830f15d8a353abcd6983e docs: Split "Special file and directories"
* efb3a142c54d6eb5d7146e9f2a684b220d0663d6 docs: Split docs for commands into sections
* e0c314fc30369eba2a647b9597bff6d05db2bcda docs: Split docs into sections for age, secret and state
* 23777d09f63695d9051a06d3825d1c3ffebc2c15 docs: Improve description for command arguments
* 5b1dbb5f1a3d9752bb4201e64ae6a4ea51754222 docs: Add example for running script on macOS update
* 4cae323e74d203e61d28916ed24f547a6fde3e6b docs: Add notes where to place 'encryption' setting
